    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_0DBCCDC5-D81B-46F1-A085-F30AEB457D25" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If enabled by your institution, you can access the Lucid Education Suite apps <a href="https://help.lucid.co/hc/en-us/articles/11970952773652-Welcome-to-Lucidchart" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Lucidchart</a> and <a href="https://help.lucid.co/hc/en-us/articles/11973407023636-Welcome-to-Lucidspark" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Lucidspark</a>. Lucidchart is an intelligent diagramming application that allows you to visualize complex ideas, systems, and processes. Lucidspark is a virtual whiteboard application that enables teams to ideate, design, and build better ideas.</p>
<p>When using Lucid for the first time, you must confirm information about your age and connect your Lucid account to your Canvas account before using Lucid in Canvas.  </p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If you cannot access Lucid, it may not be enabled for your region or by your institution. Contact your instructor for more information.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-rich-content-editor" data-step-uuid="EFFBEE44-FBDD-4CA2-AC39-CE45EC89FB09">
    <h2 id="open-rich-content-editor" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Rich Content Editor</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/393/863/original/97874299-0555-496f-91d1-13a68cab3ae3.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/393/863/medium/97874299-0555-496f-91d1-13a68cab3ae3.png" srcset="" alt="Open Rich Content Editor" height="340" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_707B6A3E-0809-4241-87D9-719A74556718" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Open the Rich Content Editor when creating or editing an announcement, assignment, discussion, page, quiz, or syllabus.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>The Rich Content Editor supports keyboard shortcuts. To view a window with a list of keyboard navigation shortcuts, click the <strong>Keyboard </strong>icon or press <strong>Alt+F8 </strong>(on a PC keyboard) or <strong>Option+F8 </strong>(on a Mac keyboard) simultaneously on your keyboard.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-lucid" data-step-uuid="84EA9B8E-40B0-4236-AEB3-145D1FE5A40A">
    <h2 id="open-lucid" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Lucid</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/374/original/d8ba6d42-d270-4c31-adf2-62e1fd8efbea.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/374/medium/d8ba6d42-d270-4c31-adf2-62e1fd8efbea.png" srcset="" alt="Open Lucid" height="89" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_CDAB062F-5BD2-486B-B098-BB971760941C" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When using Lucid for the first time, either to <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-embed-a-Lucid-document-in-the-Rich-Content-Editor-as-a/ta-p/606360" target="_blank">embed a Lucid document </a>or <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-submit-a-Lucid-document-for-a-Lucid-assignment/ta-p/606359" target="_blank">access a Lucid submission assignment</a>, you must verify information before Lucid can be used in your course.</p>
<p>To access Lucid from Rich Content Editor, click the <strong>Lucid</strong> icon [1].</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>To view the Lucid icon, you may have to click the <strong>Options </strong>icon [2]. If the icon still does not display, Lucid may not be enabled for your institution.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="verify-course-information" data-step-uuid="83489CCE-86C7-4EB0-926E-22F453E6A334">
    <h2 id="verify-course-information" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Verify Role and Age</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/376/original/cc6c96e7-a8d3-4107-9918-771665ef5503.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/376/medium/cc6c96e7-a8d3-4107-9918-771665ef5503.png" srcset="" alt="Verify Role and Age" height="499" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_A00EBF53-7B85-4FD8-9F8C-1FD19EFF9FA2" class="text-block-content">
    <p>When accessing Lucid for the first time in Canvas, you must verify information before you can use Lucid in your Canvas account.</p>
<p>Review your role [1] and select if you are over 13 years of age [2]. Then click the <strong>Next</strong> button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="request-coppa-consent" data-step-uuid="73273034-57B5-4B29-A263-6DA3A9DB37DF">
    <h3 id="request-coppa-consent" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Verify Age</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/378/original/eb9483d5-1c60-4361-9513-7dd9059b4577.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/378/medium/eb9483d5-1c60-4361-9513-7dd9059b4577.png" srcset="" alt="Verify Age" height="499" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_F4FEBC01-FFC4-4F83-8256-4BB570BF1C6D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you select that you are under 13 years of age, a prompt displays to confirm your age. To confirm your age, enter your birth date in the <strong>Birth Date</strong> field [1]. Then click the <strong>Next</strong> button [2]. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="contact-instructor" data-step-uuid="d0e00650-bf23-490b-b1e7-e36dbd114e8d">
    <h3 id="contact-instructor" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Contact Instructor</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/380/original/cc5b5fd0-bfff-4fba-9f23-2fb5960cce3f.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/380/medium/cc5b5fd0-bfff-4fba-9f23-2fb5960cce3f.png" srcset="" alt="Contact Instructor" height="450" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_058cff94-b35d-4de8-9850-b8da973199df" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have confirmed that you are younger than 13, you cannot access Lucid without permission from your institution. For help accessing Lucid, reach out to your instructor.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="connect-lucid-to-canvas" data-step-uuid="6D053C3F-AEE6-4CD0-810D-FB4E14293C11">
    <h2 id="connect-lucid-to-canvas" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Connect Lucid to Canvas</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/390/948/original/9f92e67d-be0a-428d-8913-3b8bf8fc843a.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/390/948/medium/9f92e67d-be0a-428d-8913-3b8bf8fc843a.png" srcset="" alt="Connect Lucid to Canvas" height="508" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_83614227-C64B-4277-9CE5-125021E46E90" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have confirmed you are over the age of 13 or have received permission to access the app from your institution, connect your Lucid account to your Canvas account by clicking the <strong>Connect</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="log-in-to-lucid" data-step-uuid="620E55DD-7215-43C8-87FF-7754241B30ED">
    <h2 id="log-in-to-lucid" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Log In to Lucid</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/382/original/68862a85-c5f1-4b42-a928-c6fe1e6c5cf9.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/382/medium/68862a85-c5f1-4b42-a928-c6fe1e6c5cf9.png" srcset="" alt="Log In to Lucid" height="499" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_FC4AE4D7-0E2F-40D3-9F86-D2CF16B09BF9" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you have an existing Lucid account, click the <strong>Log in</strong> button to sign in [1]. A new browser tab opens in which you can sign in to your account.</p>
<p>If you do not have a Lucid account, click the <strong>Sign up</strong> button and follow prompts to sign up for a free Lucid account [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="confirm-lucid-connection" data-step-uuid="5F79580F-D4F3-4503-B4F4-A8B740D16356">
    <h2 id="confirm-lucid-connection" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Confirm Lucid Connection</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/384/original/4935e35b-ea1d-44e9-b23c-18d0845a2ddc.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/384/medium/4935e35b-ea1d-44e9-b23c-18d0845a2ddc.png" srcset="" alt="Confirm Lucid Connection" height="499" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_8C13C317-C21A-44D6-8EE7-58411D1B8CD3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>After logging in to Lucid, your Lucid account name displays [1]. To connect your Lucid account to your Canvas account, click the <strong>Connect to Lucid</strong> button [2]. </p>
<p>To switch to a different Lucid account, click the <strong>Switch account</strong> button [3]. </p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> To view this page after logging in to Lucid, you may need to refresh your Canvas browser tab.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="confirm-lucid-education-plan" data-step-uuid="7D1B1B85-1ED5-4680-BAA0-1863EACA7612">
    <h2 id="confirm-lucid-education-plan" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Confirm Lucid Educational Plan</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/386/original/a1a2fa80-cca8-4613-a5ad-f5c2789b84a1.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/386/medium/a1a2fa80-cca8-4613-a5ad-f5c2789b84a1.png" srcset="" alt="Confirm Lucid Educational Plan" height="499" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_BC6CEE80-672E-4996-8A4D-9CCE126BA8DF" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Your Lucid account is upgraded to a free educational plan. To acknowledge, click the <strong>Continue</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-lucid" data-step-uuid="804E4FB8-A3C3-4666-874E-3D931C4EA4A7">
    <h2 id="view-lucid" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Connect Canvas to Lucid</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/388/original/08e28df7-e0c5-4ff7-a3ff-f44397b51a2c.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/388/medium/08e28df7-e0c5-4ff7-a3ff-f44397b51a2c.png" srcset="" alt="Connect Canvas to Lucid" height="499" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_33708080-0AB2-40E0-942B-D8C857FD332E" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To complete the connection between your Canvas and Lucid accounts, click the <strong>Get Started</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="grant-account-access" data-step-uuid="9400ab38-667b-4379-b25b-f64cfe438a7b">
    <h2 id="grant-account-access" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Grant Account Access</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/390/original/1371c0e2-4e4d-425b-8416-ae8fb01d30cf.png" srcset="" alt="Grant Account Access" height="1148" width="853">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_f3ba6261-6623-4155-8f46-748af4a4ff83" class="text-block-content">
    <p>A new browser tab displays. After reviewing the request for access, click the <strong>Grant Access</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-lucid-in-canvas" data-step-uuid="a91f063a-eb48-4da2-9b58-18272a59828b">
    <h2 id="view-lucid-in-canvas" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Lucid in Canvas</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/393/original/5e77ae46-b0b8-48ab-a106-a006f0103d08.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/398/393/medium/5e77ae46-b0b8-48ab-a106-a006f0103d08.png" srcset="" alt="View Lucid in Canvas" height="505" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_073226ce-cbe5-4647-afd2-0959042d1e7c" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Once your Lucid and Canvas accounts have been connected, you can view existing Lucid documents [1] and search existing documents [2].</p>
<p>To <a href="https://help.lucid.co/hc/en-us/articles/11970952773652-Welcome-to-Lucidchart#create-lucidchart-document" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">create a new Lucidchart document</a> or <a href="https://help.lucid.co/hc/en-us/articles/11973407023636-Welcome-to-Lucidspark#create-a-lucidspark-board" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">new Lucidspark board</a>, click the <strong>Add New</strong> button [3].</p>
<p>Learn more about <a href="https://help.lucid.co/hc/en-us/articles/11970952773652-Welcome-to-Lucidchart" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Lucidchart </a>and <a href="https://help.lucid.co/hc/en-us/articles/11973407023636-Welcome-to-Lucidspark" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Lucidspark</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
